{
  "stem": "9156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Nazis were starting vicious fightings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was blood all the time, and it wasn't-- and this is before they came to power.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that's very important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw, for instance, that kind of thing that happened when they took their spades off and hit people into the face.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is before they come to power.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I have to say that we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I better say this is end of 1932, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But 1933, you know, Hitler is made to be the Vice Chancellor and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- we knew that this would be a catastrophe.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, that-- unfortunately I have to--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, there were already open resistance while they were not yet in power.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The labor unions, for instance, had big signs plastered-- you know, what is it called?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A 'litfassaule' in Berlin-- L-I-T-F-A-S-S-A-U-L-E.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That means big signs of all the labor unions that joined.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We must stand against what's coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Kathe Kollwitz-- K-A-T-H-E, Kollwitz, K-O-L-L-W-I-T-Z, was one of the most wonderful artists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have my whole house is full of them, of her work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was one of the signers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the labor movement, the communists split up from it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For this kind of call, to unite against the terrible coming danger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately-- and I regret that very much-- the communists did not join in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always were separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They always had this kind of idea it has to come to the worst, then we will win.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's a dangerous thing that I don't wish anybody ever saying to me again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and labor unions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, very strong writing leaflets trying to unite the labor movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
